{"tid":1507071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【風水迷信】【燈神】11月8號會係反送中運動轉捩點","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:43:34.000Z","uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc7dca33fe86233d493cc18d94d819731e31baf","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">講左結論先：<br />\n局勢會於11月8號之後，對抗爭者不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；<br />\n林鄭落唔落台就睇呢日</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔信風水，你就當我上連登燈一燈保平安啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話唔定我勁過燒山呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理據一：</span></span><br />\n李居明2019年本《豬年運程書》p. 18<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcXxmLw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcXxmLw.jpg&h=e45e7566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭可能腳痛落台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係李居明唱好大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中又死唔中都死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理據二：</span></span><br />\n我老豆<br />\n「二五交加，二黑五黃兩粒凶星響嗰日飛去東北方；東北方代表年青人」之類<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理據三：</span></span><br />\n馮睎乾《從玄學角度談抗爭》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20190826/20755795?utm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20755795%3Futm&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b358ae80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20755795%3Futm&h=4ddc9109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20190826/20755795?utm</a><br />\n<blockquote>此卦最耐人尋味的，是世爻藏着伏神兼卦身的子孫申金（上未標示）。伏神是隱伏之力，一旦發動，可成事情轉捩點。卦身為占事主體，有提綱挈領之用。此卦伏神卦身都是子孫申金，居世爻，意義非同小可。<span style=\"color: gold;\">顧名思義，子孫即年輕人，其五行屬金，正宜剋制屬木的官鬼。</span>本來世爻丑土被二鬼夾擊，陷於困境，幸好未月沖丑，申金破墓而出，而申酉戌接連三月（新曆8月8日至11月7日），申金皆旺相。依卦推斷，9月後即使上了年紀的兄弟後勁不繼，年輕人也很可能繼續爬山。依卦推斷，9月8日至10月7日，官鬼受剋，年輕人依然活躍，相信會繼續爬山。<span style=\"color: gold;\">但由11月8日算起，入冬春兩季，尤其是農曆新年兩月，官鬼當旺，申金休囚入墓，抗爭者千萬要小心。</span>留得青山在，哪怕無柴燒，潮漲潮退，才是大海的be water。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">化解方法：</span></span><br />\n萬能key<br />\n盡人事以安天命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XVZMm2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XVZMm2.png&h=810757da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3c61c31908b405ae7c49c4eaa30362423c9e176","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4bd592787ef0dfa6db2c35df994fb7f2f7b070c9","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506824</a>"},{"pid":"bc1225f76ecf2d72b7de47760a18404def5574c3","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"&lt;文宣組入&gt; 沙田凱旋係民意核彈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dKqcCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dKqcCS</a><br />\n<br />\n#132 美孚街坊夾道歡迎義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TGVD6aMMhbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTGVD6aMMhbo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=0a6cfce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TGVD6aMMhbo</a>"},{"pid":"40afb2d1387aad7b7ff7cdf7ac4f154411519c96","tid":1507071,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b43f74b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c8ad269b209563d97d26ec722532c9ba693b8da","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e2bebe9c05433a2b396e238155c6a2bae1c6a91","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0c818e6c1323dadef9edf5feb3cd0a11ec1605e6","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2711d686a00b53af49340d1ed15c047a2b63d768","tid":1507071,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"我寧願信國師囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a29c7c0fe0c0e20a55dd26ecdf3290c0b89d4b","tid":1507071,"uid":284732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣，正氣一出，時運會變。依家抗共係順天意的正氣，雖有邪氣阻撓但不會長久。"},{"pid":"589122077bfd6eaa91fb3a386fe67f47b4e25fac","tid":1507071,"uid":68088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6f303a0cc4ecf4d15dd7f9f1763edd0f87e2fca","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66a5b6ec60d0b73205ef6e6368807565dd9cb735","tid":1507071,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"push你老竇<br />\n燒山話咗中美冷戰 香港毀滅啦"},{"pid":"609a722e382c2b64ea939215ca745f38b723a112","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"咁幾時有轉機呢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理據一</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190922/20772656/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F20772656%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=c0ce445b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F20772656%2F&h=5cabd27c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20190922/20772656/</a><br />\n<blockquote>九運正式開始於2024年，你知道那年南方配什麼卦嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「時間到了，不能不變；時間未到，欲變無力。假如你相信自己只剩下一年命，你對事情的心態，你下的一切決定，必然跟你相信自己還有五十年命不同，對不對？我希望年輕人明白，如果香港的變革需要一整個時代才能完成，他們就不該在今天輕言犧牲。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2024年，南方配的卦叫「澤火革」。這一刻，我終於明白「時代革命」的真正意思。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20190827/20756357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756357&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=65956622\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756357&h=5e40f432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20190827/20756357</a><br />\n<blockquote>五、也許最多人關心的是，林鄭何時下台？用神為官鬼申金，申寅相沖，故寅年有望沖開伏吟。寅年，即<span style=\"color: gold;\">2022年</span>，恰巧是行政長官任滿之年&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4f3871bd908bb21783a7df97229fae9b29e1f8f2","tid":1507071,"uid":259015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"66a5b6ec60d0b73205ef6e6368807565dd9cb735","tid":1507071,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"push你老竇<br />\n燒山話咗中美冷戰 香港毀滅啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"唔係喎 今次俾佢燈中<br />\n11月8號真係有大事發生 係運動轉捩點"},{"pid":"887db111ad38ebd906d0d6a9b8450856a53d6de3","tid":1507071,"uid":5893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:27:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d11eb38432f06e5a3be348862382a7c30bb3fbc","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e1be2db115ab0978718137870f5049f50288a1fc","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:14:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f0a12c6e6a465d4ed50d9e3ce728401238b8363c","tid":1507071,"uid":68088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"有冇多d之後點嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee9af71121586d5ce2210c45799fa7989e66945","tid":1507071,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0a12c6e6a465d4ed50d9e3ce728401238b8363c","tid":1507071,"uid":68088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"有冇多d之後點嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"利申其實我唔識風水<br />\n<br />\n但係之前有手足都開post講過11月8日係轉捩點<br />\n[風水救港] 8/11/2019 立冬後分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697165</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">基本上就係轉為和理非同埋搞組織</span><br />\n<br />\n至於李居明啲風水書我唔想再引用<br />\n因為佢話大灣區三年後就能成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢仲預言今年係「和平」之年<br />\n笑左"}]}